data.description: Come and see this beautifully updated home in the Dundee Estates subdivision. The current owners have taken great care to turn this home into a farmhouse masterpiece for their growing family. From the circular drive with new two car concrete parking pad, enter the home from the covered front porch, complete with porch swing, into an inviting foyer. The living room has a custom built-in entertainment center, and beautiful wood look tile flooring that spans into the dining area and kitchen, where you'll enjoy updated granite countertops with tile backsplash, farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, and a pantry. Continue through the laundry hallway into an updated flex room that could even be used as a 4th bedroom. The split-bedroom floorplan boasts a master bedroom suite with private bathroom and walk in closet and two additional sizeable bedrooms on the adjacent side of the home. You'll be able keep everyone entertained in the fully fenced back yard that comes with a 13x13 poured patio with pergola and grilling station, 11x26 paver patio with gorgeous gazebo included, above ground pool, kid's playset, and two storage buildings! All of this in a well developed neighborhood with NO HOA. Don't miss this opportunity! Come and see!A list of recent updates include: Built-ins 2020, New Roof 2020, House exterior painted 2020, Kitchen countertops 2020, New Windows 2020, Generator hookup 2020, New hot water heater 2020, New cement pad 2022, Septic tank pumped 2023. All highest and best offers are due by Tuesday, 11/28, at 8:00 p.m. est.
